**Diagram:** Progressive governance evolution from Phase 0 to Phase 3.

**Principle:** "Earn your infrastructure" - build only what complexity demands

**Phases:**
- **Phase 0 (Current):** Manual gates, 1 agent, failure log, memory logging
- **Phase 1 (Weeks 2-3):** 3-4 agents, shared conventions, reusable components
- **Phase 2 (5+ agents):** Governance subsystem, selective auto-approve, audit trail
- **Phase 3 (Complex):** Full orchestration, dedicated governance service, rollback

**Thresholds:**
- Same failure 3x → Build targeted prevention
- Recovery >1 hour → Build rollback capability
- Approval fatigue (>20/session) → Selective auto-approve
- Cost surprise → Usage monitoring
